  scalr-ctl is a command-line interface to your Scalr account

  Version 1.0 is intended to work with the new Scalr JSON API.

Install:
  $ git clone https://github.com/Scalr/pecha.git
  $ cd pecha/
  $ git checkout develop
  $ pip install --editable .
  $ . scalr-ctl-complete.sh 
  
Configure:
  $ scalr-ctl configure
  
Use:
  
  $ scalr-ctl --help
  $ scalr-ctl <tab> <tab>
